    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and<strong> ground turmeric</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p>",
