    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potato</strong> and<strong> red onion wedges</strong> to a deep baking tray with the <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>fenugreek</strong></p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
