          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pour the <strong>coconut stock</strong> over the vegetables</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the potatoes are cooked through and the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
