            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the potatoes are done, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the tray and return it to the oven for 1-2 min further or until it has started to wilt – this is your <strong>curried</strong> <strong>potato tray bake</strong></p>",
