      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>curried</strong> <strong>potato tray bake</strong> with the <strong>roasted cauliflower</strong> on top</p><p>Spoon over the <strong>mango chutney</strong> and garnish with the<strong> toasted cashew nuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
